snippet.textDisplay: OMG!!! I just heard this song on digital radio (SBS Chilll in Melbourne Australia). It is the most beautiful song I have heard for a very long time. The composition and the singing is so incredibly divine. I love everything about this song; every lyric, every beat, every emotion, every millisecond of this piece is magic. Thank you Nitin. This has moved me and changed my life. I cannot wait to see other creations you have produced.

Great version of a great track, love the mix of different sounds and the styles of singing and the different ways of using them, he is a genious! Stunning!
